ngs Target</p>\n            <div class=\"flex items-center gap-3\" data-kid=\"140\">\n              <p class=\"text-2xl font-black\" data-kid=\"141\">72%</p>\n              <div class=\"flex-1 h-2 bg-deep-navy/5 rounded-full overflow-hidden\" data-kid=\"142\">\n                <div class=\"h-full bg-green-500 w-[72%]\" data-kid=\"143\"></div>\n              </div>\n            </div>\n          </div>\n        </div>\n      </div>\n\n      \n      <div class=\"lg:col-span-4 space-y-8\" data-kid=\"144\">\n        \n        <button class=\"w-full h-32 bg-red-600 rounded-[2.5rem] shadow-[0_20px_60px_-15px_rgba(220,38,38,0.4)] flex items-center justify-center gap-6 text-white hover:scale-[1.02] active:scale-95 transition-all relative overflow-hidden group\" data-kid=\"145\">\n          <div class=\"absolute inset-0 bg-white/10 translate-x-[-100%] group-hover:translate-x-[100%] transition-transform duration-1000\" data-kid=\"146\"></div>\n          <div class=\"w-20 h-20 bg-white/20 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center animate-pulse\" data-kid=\"147\">\n            <i class=\"ti ti-sos text-5xl\" data-kid=\"148\"></i>\n          </div>\n          <div class=\"text-left\" data-kid=\"149\">\n            <h4 class=\"text-2xl font-black leading-none\" data-kid=\"150\">Emergency SOS</h4>\n            <p class=\"text-sm opacity-80 mt-1\" data-kid=\"151\">Alert all family members</p>\n          </div>\n        </button>\n\n        <div class=\"glass-card p-8 rounded-[2.5rem] space-y-6\" data-kid=\"152\">\n          <h4 class=\"text-lg font-black\" data-kid=\"153\">Family Active Now</h4>\n          <div class=\"space-y-4\" data-kid=\"154\">\n            <div class=\"flex items-center gap-4 p-3 rounded-2xl bg-white/40 hover:bg-white transition-all border border-transparent hover:border-accent/20 group\" data-kid=\"155\">\n              <div class=\"w-12 h-12 rounded-full relative\" data-kid=\"156\">\n                <img src=\"https://i.pravatar.cc/100?u=Anjali\" class=\