-400 uppercase tracking-widest mb-1\" data-kid=\"221\">Energy Grid</p>\n                   <h4 class=\"text-3xl font-black text-slate-900 tracking-tighter\" data-kid=\"222\">324.5 <span class=\"text-sm font-medium text-slate-300\" data-kid=\"223\">kWh</span></h4>\n                 </div>\n               </div>\n               <div class=\"flex items-center gap-4\" data-kid=\"224\">\n                 <div class=\"text-right hidden sm:block\" data-kid=\"225\">\n                   <p class=\"text-[10px] font-black text-emerald-600 uppercase tracking-tighter mb-2\" data-kid=\"226\">-12% MoM</p>\n                   <div class=\"w-24 h-1.5 bg-slate-100 rounded-full overflow-hidden\" data-kid=\"227\">\n                     <div class=\"h-full bg-emerald-500 w-[60%]\" data-kid=\"228\"></div>\n                   </div>\n                 </div>\n                 <button class=\"w-12 h-12 bg-white border border-slate-100 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center text-slate-400 hover:text-emerald-600 transition-colors shadow-sm\" data-kid=\"229\">\n                   <i class=\"lucide-chevron-right w-5 h-5\" data-kid=\"230\"></i>\n                 </button>\n               </div>\n            </div>\n\n            <div class=\"group bg-white border border-slate-100 hover:border-blue-200 rounded-[2.5rem] p-10 flex items-center justify-between gap-6 shadow-sm hover:shadow-xl transition-shadow\" data-kid=\"231\">\n               <div class=\"flex items-center gap-8\" data-kid=\"232\">\n                 <div class=\"w-20 h-20 bg-blue-50 rounded-3xl flex items-center justify-center text-blue-500 group-hover:bg-blue-500 group-hover:text-white transition-all\" data-kid=\"233\">\n                   <i class=\"lucide-droplet w-10 h-10\" data-kid=\"234\"></i>\n                 </div>\n                 <div data-kid=\"235\">\n                   <p class=\"text-[10px] font-black text-slate-400 uppercase tracking-widest mb-1\" data-kid=\"236\">Water Flow</p>\n                   <h4 class=\"text-3xl font-black text-slate-900 tracking-tighter\" data-kid=\"237\">11.2 <span class=\"text-sm font-medium text-slate-300\" data-kid=\"238\">kL</span></h4>\n                 </div>\n               </div>\n               <div class=\"flex items-center gap-4\" data-kid=\"239\">\n                 <div class=\"text-right hidden sm:block\" data-kid=\"240\">\n                   <p class=\"text-[10px] font-black text-emerald-600 uppercase tracking-tighter mb-2\" data-kid=\"241\">-18% MoM</p>\n                   <div class=\"w-24 h-1.5 bg-slate-100 rounded-full overflow-hidden\" data-kid=\"242\">\n                     <div class=\"h-full bg-emerald-500 w-[45%]\" data-kid=\"243\"></div>\n                   </div>\n                 </div>\n                 <button class=\"w-12 h-12 bg-white border border-slate-100 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center text-slate-400 hover:text-blue-600 transition-colors shadow-sm\" data-kid=\"244\">\n                   <i class=\"lucide-chevron-right w-5 h-5\" data-kid=\"245\"></i>\n                 </button>\n               </div>\n            </div>\n          </div>\n        </div>\n\n        \n        <div class=\"bg-emerald-600 rounded-[3rem] p-12 text-white relative overflow-hidden shadow-2xl shadow-emerald-600/20 mt-16\" data-kid=\"246\">\n           <div class=\"absolute -bottom-12 -right-12 opacity-10\" data-kid=\"247\">\n             <i class=\"lucide-sparkles w-64 h-64\" data-kid=\"248\"></i>\n           </div>\n           <div class=\"flex items-center gap-2 mb-6\" data-kid=\"249\">\n             <span class=\"px-3 py-1 bg-white/20 rounded-full text-[10px] font-black uppercase tracking-widest\" data-kid=\"250\">Earth Insight</span>\n           </div>\n           <h3 class=\"text-3xl font-bold mb-6 leading-tight\" data-kid=\"251\">Your recent conservation efforts have saved the equivalent of <span class=\"underline decoration-emerald-300 decoration-4\" data-kid=\"252\">4 mature trees</span> this month.</h3>\n           <p class=\"text-emerald-100 text-lg mb-8 opacity-80\" data-kid=\"253\">We've identified that your garden irrigation is 20% more efficient than last summer due to the new smart moisture sensors.</p>\n           <div class=\"flex gap-4\" data-kid=\"254\">\n             <button class=\"bg-white text-emerald-700 font-bold px-8 py-4 rounded-2xl hover:bg-emerald-50 transition-colors\" data-kid=\"255\">Share Progress</button>\n             <button class=\"bg-emerald-500/50 text-white font-bold px-8 py-4 rounded-2xl hover:bg-emerald-500 transition-colors border border-white/10\" data-kid=\"256\">View Detailed Report</button>\n           </div>\n        </div>\n      </div>\n    </section>\n\n  </main>\n</div>\n\n\n<script src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/gsap@3/dist/gsap.min.js\" data-kid=\"257\"></script>\n<script src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/gsap@3/dist/ScrollTrigger.min.js\" data-kid=\"258\"></script>\n<script src=\"https://unpkg.com/lucide@latest\" data-kid=\"259\"></script>\n<script data-kid=\"260\">\n  gsap.registerPlugin(ScrollTrigger);\n  lucide.createIcons();\n\n  // Navigation Logic\n  const navLinks = document.querySelectorAll('.nav-link');\n  const navPill = document.getElementById('nav-pill');\n  const sections = document.querySelectorAll('.section-block');\n\n  function updateNav() {\n    let current = \"\";\n    sections.forEach(section => {\n      const sectionTop = section.offsetTop;\n      const sectionHeight = section.clientHeight;\n      if (window.scrollY >= sectionTop - sectionHeight / 3) {\n        current = section.getAttribute('id').replace('variant-', '');\n      }\n    });\n\n    navLinks.forEach(link => {\n      link.classList.remove('text-white');\n      link.classList.add('text-white/60');\n      if (link.dataset.target === current) {\n        link.classList.remove('text-white/60');\n        link.classList.add('text-white');\n        const { offsetLeft, offsetWidth } = link;\n        gsap.to(navPill, {\n          left: offsetLeft,\n          width: offsetWidth,\n          duration: 0.4,\n          ease: \"power3.out\"\n        });\n      }\n    });\n  }\n\n  window.addEventListener('scroll', updateNav);\n  updateNav();\n\n  // Matrix Live Counter\n  const matrixTs = document.getElementById('matrix-timestamp');\n  setInterval(() => {\n    matrixTs.innerText = 'SEQ: ' + (Math.random() * 9999).toFixed(0).padStart(4, '0') + ' // ' + (Math.random() * 10).toFixed(4) + 'ms';\n  }, 80);\n\n  // Aura Animations\n  gsap.from(\"#variant-aura .aura-container\", {\n    y: 50,\n    opacity: 0,\n    duration: 1.2,\n    ease: \"power4.out\",\n    scrollTrigger: {\n      trigger: \"#variant-aura\",\n      start: \"top 80%\"\n    }\n  });\n\n  gsap.from(\"#variant-aura .aura-card\", {\n    y: 30,\n    opacity: 0,\n    duration: 0.8,\n    stagger: 0.2,\n    ease: \"power3.out\",\n    scrollTrigger: {\n      trigger: \"#variant-aura\",\n      start: \"top 60%\"\n    }\n  });\n\n  // Matrix Animations\n  gsap.from(\"#variant-matrix .col-span-12\", {\n    scale: 0.95,\n    opacity: 0,\n    duration: 1,\n    ease: \"expo.out\",\n    scrollTrigger: {\n      trigger: \"#variant-matrix\",\n      start: \"top 70%\"\n    }\n  });\n\n  // Eco Animations\n  gsap.from(\"#variant-eco h2, #variant-eco p, #variant-eco .inline-flex, #variant-eco .grid\", {\n    y: 40,\n    opacity: 0,\n    duration: 1,\n    stagger: 0.1,\n    ease: \"power2.out\",\n    scrollTrigger: {\n      trigger: \"#variant-eco\",\n      start: \"top 80%\"\n    }\n  });\n\n  // Smooth Scroll\n  document.querySelectorAll('nav a').forEach(anchor => {\n    anchor.addEventListener('click', function(e) {\n      e.preventDefault();\n      document.querySelector(this.getAttribute('href')).scrollIntoView({\n        behavior: 'smooth'\n      });\n    });\n  });\n</script>\n",
